ro 系列占订单分配约为 85%，iPhone14 Plus 订单分配约为 5%；苹果高端产品的预购在初期总是更受欢迎。从这次调查来看，今年 Pro 机型的订单占比与往年相比更高，反映了苹果的产品细分策略的变化。 截至美东时间 9 月 9 日收盘，苹果报 157.37 美元，涨幅 1.88%。较上一个交易日，苹果市值增加 468 亿美元（约 3242 亿元人民币）。 iPhone 14 系列预售太火爆！官网一度抢崩了，网友热议！苹果市值一夜飙涨 3242 亿元，这些 A 股公司深度参与苹果产业链"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b9ae56516ce7604dfbd028e09f2e564f_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/552712878"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI/qOugMGmmZ4DEAMaCDg1MTA4MzUwIPGs8JgGMAI4FkAmcgk1NTI3MTI4Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1662883932.1944182", "card_id": "Q_550563409", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "今年中秋你有吃到一些口味奇特的月饼吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "月饼是中秋佳节的传统美食，发展到今天，月饼品种更加繁多，风味因地各异。一起来晒晒你吃过的口味奇特的月饼吧。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d3a260243e2356992b06c12cb5ea6f7b_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550563409"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI/qOugMGmmZ4DEAMaCDg0NjMxMjUxIJfksZgGMAA4FEAncgk1NTA1NjM0MDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1662883932.1949816", "card_id": "Q_552095042", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本剑术真的很强吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我说的是那种实战剑术，跟中国的传统武术比呢？看日本动漫里对他们本地剑术的文化宣传，感觉还是挺帅挺强的！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d25c5095492bb063a296353d3e21b554_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type